001package edu.cnm.deepdive.zoomattendance.model.dto;
002
003import android.annotation.SuppressLint;
004import androidx.annotation.NonNull;
005import com.google.gson.annotations.Expose;
006import com.google.gson.annotations.SerializedName;
007import java.util.Date;
008
009
010public class Authentication {
011
012  @Expose
013  @SerializedName("access_token")
014  private final String token = null;
015
016  @Expose
017  @SerializedName("token_type")
018  private final String tokenType = null;
019
020  private final Date created = new Date();
021
022  @Expose
023  @SerializedName("expires_in")
024  private final int duration = 0;
025
026  @Expose
027  private final String scope = null;
028
029  public String getToken() {
030    return token;
031  }
032
033  public String getTokenType() {
034    return tokenType;
035  }
036
037  public Date getCreated() {
038    return created;
039  }
040
041  public int getDuration() {
042    return duration;
043  }
044
045  public String getScope() {
046    return scope;
047  }
048
049  public Date expiration() {
050    //noinspection PointlessArithmeticExpression
051    return new Date(created.getTime() + duration * 1000);
052  }
053
054  @SuppressLint("DefaultLocale")
055  @NonNull
056  @Override
057  public String toString() {
058    return String.format("%1$s[token=%2$s, tokentype=%3$s, scope=%4$s, created=%5$s, duration=%6$d]", getClass().getSimpleName(), token, tokenType, scope, created, duration);
059
060  }
061}
